Module Nmea.Parser

type token =
| UNIT of string
| STAR
| SPREFIX
| SLASH
| REAL of float
| NS of Coord.ns
| NAT of int
| ID of string
| HEX of int
| GPRMC
| GPGSV
| GPGSA
| GPGLL
| GPGGA
| EW of Coord.ew
| EOL
| COMMA
exception Error
val sentence : (Stdlib.Lexing.lexbuf -> token) -> Stdlib.Lexing.lexbuf -> Sentence.t
